OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774890348
OL,3,CPrime Minster launches local election
OL,4,Ccampaign in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FKeir Starmer has denied Birmingham is
OL,7,Fa "lost cause" for Labour, as he
OL,8,Flaunched the local election campaign
OL,9,Ffor 2026 in Wolverhampton.
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister met with Labour
OL,12,FParty members and supporters at City
OL,13,FCollege.
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV News Central, the
OL,16,FPrime Minister said, "We go into this
OL,17,Fin good spirits with good candidates
OL,18,Fand good Labour values."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774890348
OL,3,CPrime Minster launches local election
OL,4,Ccampaign in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FHe added, "in Birmingham we've got a
OL,7,Fpositive case to make, we know that
OL,8,Fevery vote has to be earned."
OL,10,FBirmingham City Council has been run
OL,11,Fby Labour for 14 years, but lurched
OL,12,Ffrom crisis to crisis.
OL,14,FWith an equal pay bill stretching into
OL,15,Fthe hundreds of millions, declaring
OL,16,Feffective bankruptcy, and the ongoing
OL,17,Fbin strikes.
OL,19,FAll of Birmingham's 101 seats are up
OL,20,Ffor grabs - parties need to win 52
OL,21,Fseats to gain full control.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774890348
OL,3,CPrime Minster launches local election
OL,4,Ccampaign in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FIn 2022, Labour were elected with a
OL,7,Fmajority of 16 seats, but in the last
OL,8,Ffour years that has been eroded with
OL,9,Fcouncillors either quitting the party
OL,10,For being booted out.
OL,12,FThe fragility of Labour's position in
OL,13,FBirmingham was exposed when its
OL,14,Fleader, John Cotton, failed to survive
OL,15,Fa no- confidence vote on Wednesday 25
OL,16,FMarch - at the final full council
OL,17,Fmeeting before the local elections.
OL,19,FLabour described the vote as
OL,20,F"symbolic" and said John Cotton will
OL,21,Fremain leader.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774890348
OL,3,CPrime Minster launches local election
OL,4,Ccampaign in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FKeir Starmer said he is "relishing"
OL,7,Fthe opportunity to convince voters to
OL,8,Fstick with Labour across Birmingham
OL,9,Fand the Black Country.
OL,11,FThey've currently got control of four
OL,12,Fof the largest local authorities up
OL,13,Ffor grabs in the West Midlands this
OL,14,Fyear - but all of them are at risk.
OL,16,FLabour has a fight on its hands with
OL,17,Fthe vote likely to fracture, and
OL,18,Fparties to its left and right hoping
OL,19,Fto make gains.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774890348
OL,3,CPrime Minster launches local election
OL,4,Ccampaign in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FBut Labour aren't the only party with
OL,7,Fa lot to lose come polling day. The
OL,8,FConservatives are defending three
OL,9,Funitary authorities in the West
OL,10,FMidlands: Solihull, Dudley, and
OL,11,FWalsall.
OL,13,FThe Greens, Lib Dems, and Reform UK
OL,14,Fwill be targeting all seven councils,
OL,15,Fleaving a strong likelihood that
OL,16,Fmargins for victory will be razor thin.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774890348
OL,3,CPrime Minster launches local election
OL,4,Ccampaign in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FIt's unsurprising that Keir Starmer
OL,7,Fchose Wolverhampton to start this
OL,8,Ffight. It's probably his safest
OL,9,Fcouncil in the region, with only a
OL,10,Fthird of the seats being voted on and
OL,11,Fa healthy majority.
OL,13,FIn his speech beforehand, Sir Keir
OL,14,Finsisted Labour was going out into the
OL,15,Fcampaign "on the front foot".
OL,26,@wD@JOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774890348
OL,3,CPrime Minster launches local election
OL,4,Ccampaign in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FHe concluded: "(We are) relishing the
OL,7,Fopportunity to go to doorsteps and say
OL,8,Fto people: 'Vote Labour for the
OL,9,Ffollowing reasons: vote Labour because
OL,10,Fof our values, vote Labour because of
OL,11,Four leadership. Vote Labour because it
OL,12,Fmakes a huge difference to so many
OL,13,Flives across the country."
OL,15,FThe majority of Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,16,FCabinet attended Labour's local
OL,17,Felection campaign launch.
OL,26,@nD@OOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
