OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774890348
OL,3,CPrime Minster launches local election
OL,4,Ccampaign in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves, Deputy Prime
OL,7,FMinister David Lammy, Communities
OL,8,FSecretary Steve Reed, Home Secretary
OL,9,Fand Birmingham MP Shabana Mahmood,
OL,10,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,11,Fand Work and Pensions Secretary and
OL,12,FWolverhampton MP Pat McFadden sat in
OL,13,Fthe first row of the audience for the
OL,14,Flaunch.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
