PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774890348
OL,3,CPrime Minster launches local election
OL,4,Ccampaign in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Liz Kendall,
OL,7,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander,
OL,8,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds,
OL,9,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting,
OL,10,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy and
OL,11,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper filed
OL,12,Finto the second row at the event in
OL,13,FWolverhampton.
OL,15,FWest Midlands Mayor Richard Parker was
OL,16,Falso at the event, alongside
OL,17,FBirmingham City Council Leader John
OL,18,FCotton.
OL,20,FWhat about everyone else?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
